===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# [[attire|Attire]] (e.g. [[clothing]], [[makeup]]) used to [[hide]] one's [[identity]] or [[assume]] another.
#: ''That cape and mask complete his '''disguise'''.
# {{context|figuratively|lang=en}} The [[appearance]] of something on the outside which masks what's beneath.
# The act of disguising, notably as a ploy
#: ''Any '''disguise''' may expose soldiers to be deemed enemy spies.

