===Verb===
{{en-verb|disguises|disguising|disguised}}

# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To [[change]] the [[appearance]] of (a person or thing) so as to hide, or to assume an identity.
#: ''Spies often '''disguise''' themselves.''
# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To [[prevent]] giving away or [[reveal]]ing (something secret).
#: ''He '''disguised''' his true intentions.''

